HEADWORD: Axstone
<hw>Ax"stone`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Min.)</fld>
<def>A variety of jade. It is used by some savages, particularly the
natives of the South Sea Islands, for making axes or hatchets.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Axtree</ent>⟦br⟧
